<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Final Project Submission</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #0052cc;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Final Project Submission</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello Chidi,</p>
      <p>A new final project has been submitted by <strong><%= firstName %> <%= lastName %></strong> (User ID: <%= userId %>).</p>
      <p><strong>Project URL:</strong> <a href="<%= projectUrl %>" target="_blank"><%= projectUrl %></a></p>
      <p><strong>Project Picture:</strong> See attached file.</p>
      <p>Please review the submission at your earliest convenience.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>Beks Coding Club Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Beks Coding Club. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>